{"tid":1501872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運房局：同意港鐵做法","createTime":"2019-08-24T13:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T13:37:03.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a149b4ec98188819e3d04aa78a2dc734fe2e021","tid":1501872,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"港鐵今早在市民舉行觀塘遊行前，突宣布中午起觀塘線彩虹至調景嶺站的7個站列車服務暫停，而九龍灣站至藍田站則關閉。對於外界質疑港鐵的處理手法，運房局表示，與港鐵、運輸署及警方進行風險評估後，認為在觀塘一帶進行的公眾活動，有很大可能對乘客、員工及部分車站設施構成風險。<br />\n<br />\n運房局同意港鐵公司提出關閉部分車站，以保障乘客及員工安全，及防止車站設施被破壞。當局指，<span style=\"color: red;\">今次暫停服務並非因港鐵人為錯誤或機件故障所致，港鐵公司毋需按服務表現安排罰款</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1075742/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1075742%2F&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=a3223ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1075742%2F&h=def972c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1075742/</a>"},{"pid":"aead033f147684696dcff2ab8102065063ce3f73","tid":1501872,"uid":272952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5353ed6959fdc916583eec036a3243fd1a8b6aa4","tid":1501872,"uid":271088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"hight court 單野一定唔可以放過，因為只要兩個原因<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501638</a>"},{"pid":"a1997ccf414d7422ed62d3794c8a78c89ee82a4d","tid":1501872,"uid":36551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"政府持股75%，自己同意自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef923f785646cf035f3113632b6703837792a7c","tid":1501872,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"有趣<br />\n根本好似自問自答咁"}]}